description:

- Comes with 4 extra rings for multiple applications
- Apply just like you would your feathers
- Standard Length 12" 
- Extra Long 14'+
- Hand made in the uk

name: Feather Hair Lulu
description:
Hand made Feather Hair Lulu

Have the best of both worlds with our feather hair lulu's, a beautiful wrap with feathers on the end. Pop them in with a micro ring or clip for a no fuss hair wrap that will last for up to six weeks. 

- Around 12" long including feathers good for all hair lengths. 
- Comes with 4 extra rings for multiple applications
- Feather Ray fine quality feathers on the end
- Apply just like you would your feathers
- Hand made in the uk
- Order by 12pm & your feathers should be dispatched by first class signed for by Royal Mail to arrive within 2 working days
